import React from 'react'
import { Button, Form, FormGroup, Label, Input } from 'reactstrap'

export const Login = () => {
  return (
    <Form inline>
      <FormGroup>
        <Label for='exampleEmail' hidden>
          Email
        </Label>
        <Input
          type='email'
          name='email'
          id='exampleEmail'
          placeholder='Email'
        />
      </FormGroup>{' '}
      <FormGroup>
        <Label for='examplePassword' hidden>
          Password
        </Label>
        <Input
          type='password'
          name='password'
          id='examplePassword'
          placeholder='Password'
        />
      </FormGroup>{' '}
      <Button>Submit</Button>
    </Form>
  )
}
